sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant controller as CourtController
    participant service as CourtService
    participant db as DataSource

    User->>controller: GET /courts/:id
    activate controller

    controller->>service: findOne(id)
    activate service

    service->>db: find court by id
    activate db

    Note right of db: Filter: withDeleted = false<br/>Load: province, district (eager)

    db-->>service: court
    deactivate db

    service-->>controller: CustomApiResponse~Court~
    deactivate service

    controller-->>User: HTTP 200 with court
    deactivate controller
